source.instructions:
Have a look at our `index.html` and `style.css` in the top left hand pane as well as at the preview underneath it.

We ask you to change the CSS so that:

1) The nav on the bottom should be different than the one from the top. Use descendant selector to target the `li` in `#footer-nav`.
This `li` should have a style like:

```css
display: inline;
background-color:transparent;
margin:2px;
padding:0px
font-size:80%;
```

2) The `h2` which has a class of `selected` should not be in bold like the other `selected` elements. Instead it should be like: 

```css
background-color:lightsalmon;
font-weight:normal;
margin-left:40px;
```

3) Again the `p` which has a class of `selected` should not be in bold. It should be like this :

```css
background-color:lightsalmon;
font-weight:normal;
margin-left:60px;
color:black;
```

That's it  ... Good luck !
